title: Predicting Taylor's Moves In 2022! (13's Version)
description:
Taylor Swift always has tricks up her sleeve but we think we know what she's planning for this year! We have thoughts on her upcoming tour, which album is going to be next, and the big announcement that she is going to make!
What do you think she'll be doing this year? Let us know all of your thoughts and theories!
